    "longBusinessSummary": "Allied Cooperative Insurance Group engages in cooperative insurance operations and related activities in the Kingdom of Saudi Arabia. The company operates through Medical Insurance; Motor Insurance; Property Insurance; Engineering Insurance; and Other Insurance segments. It offers individual insurance products, such as health insurance for domestic workers, medical malpractice insurance, vehicle insurance, and travel care insurance; and corporate health insurance, health insurance for small groups, and marine insurance. The company also provides engineering insurance, including insurance against breakdown of machinery and equipment in factories; securing buildings and contractors' equipment; insurance against all installation risks; insurance for electronic devices; insured damage; and insurance against loss of profits due to machinery breakdown. In addition, it offers fire and perils insurance, shopkeepers insurance, housing insurance, and property insurance against risks; and personal accident insurance comprising personal accidents and general civil liability. The company was founded in 2007 and is based in Riyadh, the Kingdom of Saudi Arabia.",
